============================================================
03 – BIG 5 MATCHUP ANALYSIS (04_03.csv)
============================================================

This section focuses on head-to-head analysis between the
top Premier League clubs:
- Arsenal
- Manchester City
- Manchester United
- Chelsea
- Liverpool

The goal is to examine how elite teams perform directly
against each other in terms of:
- scoring behavior
- competitiveness
- physical intensity
- overall matchup dynamics

Unlike the previous section, which analyzed teams
individually, this stage focuses on direct rivalries and
pairwise interactions between top clubs.

The analysis combines ranking charts, dominance metrics,
and heatmap visualizations to provide a deeper understanding
of elite football match behavior.


------------------------------------------------------------
Included Visualizations
------------------------------------------------------------

- Big 5 Matchups – Average Goals
- Big 5 Matchups – Intensity Score
- Big 5 Matchups – Win Dominance
- Big 5 Matchup Performance Heatmap


------------------------------------------------------------
Key Analytical Insights
------------------------------------------------------------

The analysis reveals several important patterns regarding
elite Premier League rivalries:

- Matchups such as Arsenal vs Liverpool and Liverpool vs
  Manchester City produce the highest average number of
  goals, indicating highly offensive and open gameplay.

- Certain fixtures, particularly Chelsea vs Manchester
  United and Arsenal vs Manchester United, demonstrate
  increased physical intensity through higher numbers of
  fouls and cards.

- Some rivalries remain highly balanced, with nearly equal
  win rates between teams, while others show clear
  long-term dominance by one side.

- Heatmap analysis highlights differences in playing style
  across matchups:
  - some games emphasize attacking football
  - others involve more defensive or physical gameplay

- Offensive metrics such as shots and corners strongly
  correlate with high-scoring matchups, reflecting more
  aggressive attacking strategies.


